---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us - Medical Negligence Lawyers Directory"
  description="Learn about our comprehensive directory of medical negligence lawyers across Australia and how we help connect victims with experienced legal professionals."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900 to-blue-700 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4">About Us</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-blue-100">
        Connecting medical negligence victims with experienced legal professionals across Australia
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Medical Negligence Lawyers Directory was created to help victims of medical malpractice find qualified legal representation across Australia. We understand that dealing with the aftermath of medical negligence can be overwhelming, and finding the right lawyer to represent your case is crucial.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 mt-12">What We Do</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Our directory provides a comprehensive listing of medical negligence lawyers organized by state and city, making it easy for you to find local legal professionals who specialize in medical malpractice cases. Whether you're dealing with surgical errors, misdiagnosis, birth injuries, medication errors, or hospital negligence, our directory can help you connect with experienced lawyers who can assess your case.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 mt-12">Why Choose Our Directory</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Comprehensive Coverage</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              We list medical negligence lawyers across all Australian states and territories, ensuring you can find local representation no matter where you are.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Easy to Navigate</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Our intuitive interface allows you to browse by state and city, making it simple to find lawyers in your area.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Detailed Profiles</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Each lawyer listing includes contact information and details about their practice, helping you make an informed decision.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Free to Use</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Our directory is completely free for those seeking legal representation. There are no fees to browse or contact lawyers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 mt-12">Types of Cases We Cover</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>Surgical errors and post-operative complications</li>
          <li>Misdiagnosis or delayed diagnosis</li>
          <li>Birth injuries and obstetric negligence</li>
          <li>Medication errors and prescription mistakes</li>
          <li>Hospital-acquired infections</li>
          <li>Anesthesia errors</li>
          <li>Emergency room negligence</li>
          <li>Nursing home abuse and neglect</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-6 my-8">
          <p class="text-gray-800">
            <strong>Important:</strong> This directory provides listings of medical negligence lawyers for informational purposes only. We do not provide legal advice or endorse any specific lawyer or law firm. We recommend consulting with multiple lawyers to find the best fit for your specific case.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 mt-12">Get Started</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Start by browsing our directory by state or use the search function to find lawyers in your city. Each listing provides contact information so you can reach out directly to discuss your case. Many lawyers offer free initial consultations to assess your situation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
